race.comment: CANYA HANDLE IT (8) comes here after a sizzling Grade 5 win at this track over 400m in 22.58. In winning form and can measure up again. MISS ELPHABA (2) hit the frame two back then broke through last time by 1.5 lengths (23.51) at this track over 400m. Drawn well off an inside draw. Has placed two times at this track. Expecting another bold showing. ZIPPING LYNDY (4) bolted in last time, scoring by 3.5 lengths in slick time (22.75) to take a Grade 5 in a new PB this course and distance. In form and must include in calculations. SONGAR PEARL (1) warrants respect following a recent placing at big odds.
